summary: SummaryL'Or√©al Paris' Voluminous Panorama Washable Mascara is a volumizing mascara that is clump, flake, and smudge-resistant, for up to 24hrs wear. The multi-level bristle brush easily grabs each lash, inner to outer corner for even application from root to tip.
details: DetailsBenefitsCorner to corner panoramic volume. Lashes are so fanned out eye look is up to 1.4x biggerTheir volumizing mascara is smudge resistant, clump resistant, and flake resistant with up to 24 hour wearThe multi level bristle brush easily grabs each lash from inner to outer corner allowing for even application from root to tip5 percent Stretchflex Complex formula wraps each lash giving you flexible, defined, lash by lash volumeOphthalmologist tested. Suitable for sensitive eyes. Suitable for contact lens wearers. Easy to removeItem 2617241How To UseUse multi-level bristle brush to easily grab each lash from inner to outer corner fanning out lashes.To safeguard L'Oreal purity, reserve this product for your personal use. Treat the applicator with the hygienic care you give your eyes. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle. Do not dilute mascara with water, saliva, or any other substance. Cap tightly after use. reviews.headline: not volumizing or lengthening
reviews.comments:
i don't see a big difference of the volume or length of my lashes using this product. it holds a curl and separate lashes without being clumpy so i use it as a base or "primer" and use a different lengthening mascara on my roots.

i still use this product and it is helpful for priming my lashes but it's not as impressive as advertised

reviews.headline: Beautiful lashes
reviews.comments: I normally use this in waterproof but had eye surgery so i got this because its easier to remove until my eyes healed. Let me say this mascara made my eyelashes full, long and curled and didnt flake or smudge. You should try this if you prefer non waterproof cause its a good one.

reviews.headline: The best mascara ever!!
reviews.comments: I have tried so many mascaras and I have finally found my holy grail mascara. I'm someone with long lashes but they are stick straight, other mascaras I curl my lashes, apply, and it looks great but then they fall within 5 minutes and I'm back to looking like I have no lashes. This mascara on the other hand holds a curl! It almost looks like I have fake eyelashes on but they're my real lashes. It's also super longlasting, I use the regular (not waterproof) and it still holds up even if I get wet or cry (if fully submerged in water it will come off though). Please never stop making this mascara it's so good!!

faceoff_positive.comments: As someone who lacks being blessed with thick long lashes, finding the perfect mascara that effectively provides volume and length can be a challenge. The L'Or√©al Paris Voluminous Panorama Mascara has quickly become a staple in my beauty routine. With its incredible formula delivering dramatic voluminous long lashes for extended worry free long wear, this mascara has exceeded my expectations. The mascara arrived in a beautiful, luxurious gold container. The textured tube makes it easier to hold, and the size is convenient for travel. One of the key feautures that make it stand out are it's impressive powerhouse formula, with it's potent 5% Stretchflex formula, it effectively coats each lash individually and evenly, while enhancing not only, volume & length, but curl as well. When applying, I noticed a significant improvement with the tapered wand feauturing a multi-level silicone bristled brush that captures each lash & fans them elegantly. The gentle tapered brush easily allows for precisely reaching the inner and outer corners for even clean application successfully while other mascara brushes fail from shape. However, I have short, sparse, straight eyelashes, and with just a few applications, the mascara effectively delivers perfect length, volume, and curl for all-day wear. The mascara can easily be layered for buildable, clump, and flake-free wear while allowing for a customizable makeup look to your own individual preference. The pleasant rich black in shade blackest black, adding depth and intensity, helps make eyes stand out and enhances my overall makeup look. I really enjoy this mascaras formula, its lightweight and creamy texture, help it to apply smoother while effortlessly glides on the lashes and dries quickly without leaving any smudges, looking fresh all day long. Despite its powerful ingredients, it's gentle on the eyes without causing irritation or sensitivity. After all-day wear, it's easily removable with a makeup remover. Gifted complimentary.
faceoff_positive.headline: Achieve Sensational Voluminous & Elongated Lashes!

faceoff_negative.comments: When you open the package and actually handle the mascara, the weight of it is a bit deceiving. The formula is very light, or they just don't put a lot of product in this massive tube. I like that the mascara doesn't have a strong odor and it actually goes on smooth, the wand is nice, but it certainly wasn't volumizing. I wouldn't say it's voluminous. It gives me a bit of length, but doesn't give me volume. I tried layering it to see if that would help, but I found it didn't. It's a bit disappointing. I certainly would continue to use this mascara as it separates and coats my lashes well, but if you're looking for an actual volumizing mascara, I don't think this is it.
faceoff_negative.headline: Not as volumizing as expected
